    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## SAP SuccessFactors → Onboarding Survey + Telegram Alert\nTriggered by SF Integration Center when a candidate completes their onboarding document signature. Sends the candidate a pre-filled Google Form survey email and alerts your HR Telegram group that the record is waiting in Manage Pending Hire.\n\n**Requirements:** SuccessFactors with Integration Center · SMTP or Gmail credential · Telegram bot (via @BotFather) · a Google Form",
        "height": 192,
        "width": 720
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -640,
        -128
      ],
