      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Setup\n1. Attach a Basic Auth credential to the Webhook node\n2. In \"Build Survey Link\", replace <YOUR_GOOGLE_FORM_ID> and <GOOGLE_FORM_EMAIL_ENTRY_ID> (use your form's \"Get pre-filled link\")\n3. Add your SMTP credential + sender email on the email node\n4. Add your Telegram bot credential + chat ID\n5. In SF Integration Center, create an outbound integration to the production webhook URL, mapping fields: Email, FirstName, LastName",
